trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> objects.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref> class.
Adds the supplied <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> to the current collection.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> to add.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref> index at which the value has been added.
Determines whether the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref> contains a specific element.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> to locate in the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref>.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref> contains the specified value; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Copies the elements of the current collection into the supplied array, starting at the specified array index.
The one-dimensional <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> array that is the destination of the elements copied from the current collection.
The array must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in `array` at which copying begins.
Determines the index of a specific item in the collection.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> to locate in the collection.
The zero-based index of the first occurrence of value within the entire , if found; otherwise, -1.
Inserts an element into the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref> at the specified index.
The zero-based index at which `value` should be inserted.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> to insert.
Gets or sets the element at the specified index.
The zero-based index of the element.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> at the specified index.
Removes the first occurrence of a specific object from the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref>.
The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItem"></xref> to remove from the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionItemCollection"></xref>.
